Use case

Class: School
Contains all Admins
Contains all Students
Contains all Courses
Calculates semester information(Ends semester, forces GPA calculations in Student).
Handles Login


Class: Admin
Creates Course and adds to Courses
Creates Student and adds to Students
Registers Students to Courses
Edits Course
Edits Admin
Edits Student
Views Course
Views Admin
Views Student
Views Tests

Class: Student
Contains information: Student’s name, student’s ID, registered courses, GPA
Updates GPA
Views Course
Views Tests

Class: Course
Contains information: Course ID, Course Time, Semester, Course Description, Exams
Calculates grade information for course (A,B,ect)
